						<summary>

						<p>On the <hi rend="italic">gōpura</hi> of the Chōḷēśvara temple, right of entrance.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Sundarapāṇḍyadēva: Year 8, Aṟpaśi.</hi></p>						

						<p>This record registers a royal order addressed to the authorities of several temples in Poṉṉamarāpatippaṟṟu restraining them from using the water in Iḍaṅgamikāman, unlike before.</p>						

						<p>Cf. Inscriptions (Texts) of the Pudukkottai State, No. 513.</p>						

						</summary>
